Tools and Technologies used:
Java 8
Maven
SLF4J
GitHUb
Rest Assured framework for api automation
IntelliJ IDEA IDE
cucumber



How to Run All tests  at a time in MAC:
-> go to inside project
-> open mac terminal
-> enter mvn test


How to Run one testcase  at a time in MAC:
-> go to inside project
 src->test->java->runner
-> run Runner class

Test reports after test execution
-> go to inside project
 target->Destination->index.html


